    "title": "Adidas India is Hiring: E-commerce Executive (Junior)",
    "description": "Grow your career with Adidas India! We are hiring a E-commerce Executive for our Navi Mumbai team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Adidas India:\nAdidas India is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n• Create engaging content for product pages and social media\n• Manage marketplace relationships with Amazon, Flipkart, and Meesho\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n• Build and maintain affiliate and influencer marketing programs\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in Email Marketing\n• Proficiency in WooCommerce\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in Affiliate Marketing\n• Proficiency in Performance Marketing\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Flexible working hours\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Navi Mumbai, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Adidas India!",
